body:
@Vishurao06 You're installing a wheel for Python 3.5. `tensorflow-1.0.0cp35-cpm35` where **cp35** is the version it was compiled to. 
You need the corresponding wheel for Python 3.6 that you can download [here](http://ci.tensorflow.org/view/Nightly/job/nightly-win/M=windows,PY=36/lastSuccessfulBuild/artifact/cmake_build/tf_python/dist/tensorflow-1.2.0rc2-cp36-cp36m-win_amd64.whl)
